@zangyk Yep, right. But it is not so difficult to parse this SQL for Oracle. If you would like to take part in, here is a solution needing your contribution.

Add the grammar definition fo this SQL to `shardingsphere-sql-parser/shardingsphere-sql-parser-dialect/shardingsphere-sql-parser-oracle/src/main/antlr4/imports/oracle/DMLStatement.g4` referring Oracle documment.

Look forward to your joining.

